Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.68,0:04:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在打工的餐厅遇上优子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.88,0:04:40.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在打工的餐厅遇上优子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.55,0:04:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子是人妻，很温柔，满溢着成熟味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.89,0:04:55.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（打工处认识的美丽太太）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.25,0:05:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白木太太...在休息吧?放轻松
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.67,0:05:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的便当...不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.74,0:05:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快收下吧，有人来会不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.61,0:05:46.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快吧...也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.29,0:05:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但，为什么要为我作便当?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.42,0:06:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道，没办法放下你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.83,0:06:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正志一个人住吧?也没好好吃饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.71,0:06:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有你的便当就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.65,0:06:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能仗着年轻，你还有闪耀的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.52,0:06:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧\N当然，接下来还有许多要经历的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.07,0:06:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能一直喝吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.54,0:06:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个一次只能一杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.22,0:06:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我更年期到了，很渴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.63,0:07:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这张卡还是只能一次一杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.57,0:07:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果要水的话我马上拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.71,0:07:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你当我傻了吗?明明有卡还这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.32,0:07:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没那么想...客人，怎么了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.06,0:07:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就他不让我用张卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.73,0:07:52.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他乱说的...客人，要再追加一杯吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.41,0:07:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.75,0:08:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以了，这里交给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.16,0:08:21.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么客人要点什么?...和刚的一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.77,0:08:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样就好吗?...嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.31,0:08:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论什么麻烦，都有大人的解决方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.25,0:08:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有优子在，就越来越想上班了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.46,0:08:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.67,0:09:03.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用优子来自慰，有些罪恶感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.08,0:09:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我停不下来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.11,0:09:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再去店里看到优子会不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.34,0:10:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.02,0:10:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有家的味道，真受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.29,0:10:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子作的便当超好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.96,0:10:34.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考虑到我的健康以蔬菜为中心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.90,0:10:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有优子那样的太太，人生就幸福了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.12,0:10:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.46,0:10:59.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.26,0:11:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店长，怎么了?\N你去补些东西，店里交给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.48,0:11:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这样子了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.22,0:11:29.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.11,0:11:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白木太太怎么了?...正志，帮帮我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.05,0:12:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事? \N我换了新手机，但不会用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.33,0:12:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.13,0:12:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正志知道吗?\N大致上是...那拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.47,0:12:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想在选单设信箱\N但选单一直出不来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.28,0:12:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么用呢?...这里这么开?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.35,0:12:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么用，选单就会出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.23,0:12:45.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里啊?再来次...就这么用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.90,0:12:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选单就会出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.84,0:12:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此，好行...没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.38,0:13:01.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么回来要怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.05,0:13:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就回上一页...这里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.86,0:13:08.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里就可以了啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.39,0:13:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞，你看我用一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.87,0:13:25.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就会回上一页?...对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.61,0:13:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选单就是这里?...对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.15,0:13:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.76,0:13:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那信箱呢?选单的这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.70,0:13:54.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里啊，正志好行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.37,0:13:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 ...为什么知道呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.57,0:14:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都知道的...好行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.32,0:14:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么啊，那这里呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.39,0:14:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么用就会回到原来的画面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.86,0:14:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好行，一下就知道怎么用了.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.01,0:14:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真容易明白，谢谢...没什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.21,0:14:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.42,0:14:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么就可以了嘛?谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.89,0:14:52.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的得救了，正志谢谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.23,0:15:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又年轻又值得这赖\N那种程度的0K啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.37,0:15:07.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那工作也要加油了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.78,0:15:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次谢谢你好了\N谢谢?...因为你教我了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.99,0:15:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么大不了的...说吧，要什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.73,0:15:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么好呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.73,0:15:35.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然去你家作菜...作菜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.34,0:15:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗? ...可以啊，想吃什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.08,0:15:51.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖哩饭啦...咖哩?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.89,0:15:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了，我还会放满满的菜哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.36,0:16:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.24,0:16:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了，谢谢，真开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.84,0:16:20.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和优子的距离感几乎没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.45,0:16:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是我也不知道会如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.39,0:16:30.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过优子真的好香啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.53,0:16:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3天后，我和优子一起放假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.27,0:16:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子真的来我家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.63,0:17:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真性感啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.71,0:17:20.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.25,0:17:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么...骗人，你说了什么吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.26,0:17:43.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快说，僵在这里等等会饿的\N就没说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.74,0:17:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑的，你真认真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.28,0:17:59.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真担心你未来交不交得到女友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.35,0:18:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有喜欢的人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.84,0:18:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.71,0:18:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢优子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.86,0:18:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啦正志...我喜欢优子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.93,0:18:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.00,0:18:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正志，不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.74,0:18:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正志，不啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.14,0:19:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子...就说不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.88,0:19:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受不了了....正志，不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.77,0:19:33.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托，不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.38,0:19:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好香啊...正志，不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.65,0:19:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.05,0:19:46.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正志
