Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.59,0:20:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢优子...不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.73,0:21:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.13,0:21:08.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.42,0:21:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正志...真美，优子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.75,0:21:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正志...真美，优子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.38,0:21:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.46,0:22:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子真美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.82,0:22:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.36,0:22:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手...我受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.28,0:23:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.17,0:23:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:30.07,0:24:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.97,0:24:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:59.17,0:25:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好滑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:18.12,0:25:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想看啊，不都湿了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:29.33,0:25:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害羞，不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:02.03,0:26:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:31.39,0:26:34.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
