Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:17.97,0:27:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:24.51,0:27:26.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:52.14,0:27:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直好想用呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:30.91,0:29:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正志...优子，你好美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:03.07,0:30:04.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都好美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:55.92,0:30:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害羞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:07.27,0:31:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:18.08,0:31:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美呢，优子
