Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:38.10,1:31:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个星期没见了，也不接电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:44.11,1:31:47.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整个人都无心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:05.99,1:32:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:13.60,1:32:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早，茶渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:17.07,1:32:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店长今天请假，好像发高烧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:22.81,1:32:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你会在吗?\N我还有事，之后就交给白木
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:33.09,1:32:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:42.83,1:32:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天一定要说，这情况让我变得怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:28.74,1:33:30.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白木太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:33.42,1:33:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我一起弄吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:40.76,1:33:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别在意，我自己可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:53.70,1:34:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于看到优子，但一直在躲我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:04.38,1:34:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔们真的结束了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:43.89,1:34:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:57.90,1:35:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么躲我?...才没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:06.04,1:35:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人，你在躲我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:12.71,1:35:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后悔和我搞了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:22.99,1:35:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没后悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:29.53,1:35:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但，还是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:36.47,1:35:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢优子
