Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:19.24,1:37:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我的心情，不要躲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:35.92,1:37:37.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很烦恼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:39.39,1:37:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想着正志对我不是真心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:45.53,1:37:51.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我受不了了
